Q3. Which language is used in Gradle build scripts?
Groovy DSL
Kotlin DSL
Q4. Which tool is preferred for Android development?

Gradle is the official build tool for Android.

Summary
Gradle is a modern build automation tool.
Uses Groovy/Kotlin DSL instead of XML.
Faster and more flexible than Maven.
Maven is easier and more standardized.
Gradle is better for large and performance-focused projects.